ow message processing** using the quick filter.\n3. Select the **Workflow message processing** batch job.\n4. Click **Edit** in the action pane.\n5. Select the **Critical Job** check box.\n6. Click **Save** in the action pane.\n","nodes":[{"content":"Configure the Workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","nodes":[{"pos":[0,63],"content":"Configure the Workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","nodes":[{"content":"Configure the Workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","pos":[0,63]}]}],"pos":[31,95],"yaml":true},{"content":"Configure the workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","nodes":[{"pos":[0,63],"content":"Configure the workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","nodes":[{"content":"Configure the workflow Message Processing batch job as critical","pos":[0,63]}]}],"pos":[108,172],"yaml":true},{"pos":[1129,1192],"content":"Configure the Workflow message processing batch job as critical","linkify":"Configure the Workflow message processing batch job as critical","nodes":[{"content":"Configure the Workflow message processing batch job as critical","pos":[0,63]}]},{"content":"The workflow system uses various batch jobs.","pos":[1237,1281]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Workflow message processing<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> is an important batch job used to process workflow messages.","pos":[1282,1374],"source":"**Workflow message processing** is an important batch job used to process workflow messages."},{"content":"If workflow is a key component of your organization, you should consider configuring the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Workflow message processing<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> batch job as critical.","pos":[1375,1518],"source":" If workflow is a key component of your organization, you should consider configuring the **Workflow message processing** batch job as critical."},{"content":"Configuring the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Workflow message processing<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> batch job as critical ensures that the system acti